snippet.title: EPI 60 SOAPS IN REVIEW KAROLINA SIVAS & AMBER SMITH BROKEN AT LOVE & SOAP RECAPS
snippet.description:
Source:
https://www.spreaker.com/user/take2radio/epi-60-soaps-in-review-karolina-sivas-am

WELCOME TO TAKE 2 RADIO SOAPS IN REVIEW & HAVE YOU HEARD? THE LATEST IN SOAP NEWS! This show is on the 2nd & 4th THURSDAY of the month at 7PM EASTERN TIME! 

 ***SPECIAL SHOW*** EPISODE 60: Take 2 Radio Soaps in Review & Have You Heard? The latest in soap news: THURSDAY, JUNE 28TH at 7pm eastern: We'll speak with actress, producer, writer, Karolina Sivas, and actress, Amber  about their series Broken at Love Season 3! Watch season 1 & 2 on brokenatlovetheseries.com  

About Broken at Love: is a SAG-AFTRA online dramedy set around an idealistic college girl, Vivienne "Vivie" Taylor (Karolina Sivas), who gets the rare opportunity to meet her celebrity crush, a professional "bad boy" tennis player named Holden Gregory (Rob Healy) and her life is turned upside down as a result. What begins as Vivie's crush soon evolves into much more, with friends, family, and competing love interests further complicating things along the way.

JOIN PAM, CAROLYN, CANDICE & ANTHONY as they discuss what's been happening on The Bold and the Beautiful, Days of Our Lives, General Hospital, and The Young and the Restless
